Baiklah.

128
00:10:19,401 --> 00:10:22,815
Ada Judith dan RJ.
Mereka anak-anak, sama sepertimu.

129
00:10:22,839 --> 00:10:25,731
Ada Connie, Yehezkiel.

130
00:10:25,755 --> 00:10:27,559
Ada seorang perempuan bernama Carol.

131
00:10:27,583 --> 00:10:29,605
Kedengarannya bagus.

132
00:10:29,629 --> 00:10:31,674
