tak pernah jadi kesukaanku.

207
00:17:46,891 --> 00:17:50,088
Saat aku pertama kali tiba di Sarang,

208
00:17:50,112 --> 00:17:53,072
aku kehilangan istri dan anakku.

209
00:17:54,508 --> 00:17:58,401
Yang ingin kulakukan hanyalah mati.

210
00:17:58,425 --> 00:18:01,926
